{"tid":2322402,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TMA 2020︱Sana@TWICE需隔離缺席　王嘉爾中文提粉絲注意身體","createTime":"2020-12-12T09:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T10:16:50.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e71b66dab277a55ba2db842c1edd6cf506b5363e","tid":2322402,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"韓國大型頒獎禮The Fact Music Awards 2020（TMA 2020）今天（12日）舉行，可是礙於新冠疫情關係，頒獎禮改以網上直播形式進行。BTS防彈少年團、Super Junior、MAMAMOO、IZ*ONE、ITZY、GOT7等都組合有率先現身紅地氈，氣氛熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n雖然臨近年尾，歌手們都相當忙碌，加上今年現場沒有觀眾粉絲參與，但一樣無阻偶像歌手們的興緻，就連久未合體現身的Super Junior狀態也相當好！早前TWICE成員Sana因與請夏見面後，被視為新冠肺炎緊密接觸者，正在隔離當中，因此今晚只有7位成員出席，氣勢稍弱。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201212/414463007968464896379084.jpeg/2ysbXJ21ujVMbDCR15f9SDDIndCAzOS6hLq33YS6t90?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201212%2F414463007968464896379084.jpeg%2F2ysbXJ21ujVMbDCR15f9SDDIndCAzOS6hLq33YS6t90%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=d1f4f80a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於今晚頒獎禮進行全球直播，因此GOT7用上韓、中、英及泰文向世界各地粉絲問好，Jackson王嘉爾則用中文提議粉絲疫情期間要注意身體，相當貼心。Super Junior早前已預告今晚將有新歌舞台，加上希澈也宣布參與表演，相信粉絲必定非常期待。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201212/414463164436975616860235.jpeg/LBkNr0edLVqlMhk4u-pWSUIeEq3XTPnDSObFsEjmxbA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201212%2F414463164436975616860235.jpeg%2FLBkNr0edLVqlMhk4u-pWSUIeEq3XTPnDSObFsEjmxbA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=8e002666&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a79ff379a3ca396170da4bf8582fb060f67c0233","tid":2322402,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201212/414463690025603072724853.jpeg/ZX-5nSvAOBpYVFS7dSTCjmPyZp4QvfALdTyj4HU8o-A?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201212%2F4